{
  "texts": [
    "The model might generate responses that align with popular beliefs or prevailing sentiments rather than relying on accurate and evidence-based information [25].",
    "This has implications for its reliability as a source of information, especially in matters of public health and safety [26].",
    "Inconsistency in responses poses another challenge.ChatGPT may offer differing responses to the same inquiry made at different times [23].",
    "This variability may reduce the reliability and coherence of the information provided and create confusion for users seeking accurate and reliable answers.",
    "Finally, the risk of false references is another concern."
  ]
}